{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"func"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"addGeoJSONSourceFeatures"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"forSourceId"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"sourceId"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"String","preciseIdentifier":"s:SS"},{"text":", ","kind":"text"},{"text":"features","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": ["},{"text":"Feature","kind":"typeIdentifier","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.mapbox.MapboxMaps\/documentation\/MapboxMaps\/Feature","preciseIdentifier":"s:10MapboxMaps7Featurea"},{"text":"], ","kind":"text"},{"text":"dataId","kind":"externalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:SS","text":"String","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"? = nil)"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The identifier of the style source.","type":"text"}]}],"name":"sourceId"},{"name":"features","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An array of GeoJSON features to be added to the source.","type":"text"}]}]},{"name":"dataId","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"An arbitrary string used to track the given GeoJSON data.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"content":[{"text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The add operation will be scheduled and applied on a GeoJSON serialization queue.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"In order to capture events when actual data is drawn on the map please refer to Events API"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and listen to "},{"code":"onSourceDataLoaded","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" (optionally pass the "},{"type":"codeVoic